OL,4,Chim barefoot and alone three miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FA Police sergeant has been demoted
OL,8,Fafter a man left barefoot in the
OL,9,Fstreet by officers three miles from
OL,10,Fhis home was killed in a hit-and-run.
OL,12,FGareth Roper, 35, had been taken away
OL,13,Fby officers in the early hours of New
OL,14,FYear's Day 2022 after his wife
OL,15,Freported he was "acting in a strange
OL,16,Fmanner".
OL,18,FBut nine minutes later they de-
OL,19,Farrested him.
