OL,7,FWhen he got out of the police van in
OL,8,FWigan he was only wearing his boxer
OL,9,Fshorts. His clothing, which had been
OL,10,Fhanded to officers by a relative, was
OL,11,Fleft on the road close to his feet.
OL,13,FTwenty four minutes later he was hit
OL,14,Fby a car driven by Jamie Evans, 32,
OL,15,Fwhere he died at the scene.
OL,17,FA police misconduct hearing found
OL,18,FSergeant David Wood breached the
OL,19,Fpolice professional standards.
