OL,7,FIt ruled this amounted to gross
OL,8,Fmisconduct and he was demoted to the
OL,9,Frank of PC.
OL,11,FThe panel also found misconduct
OL,12,Fagainst a former Sergeant and two PCs
OL,13,Finvolved in the arrest, the
OL,14,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe two PCs will undergo reflective
OL,18,Fpractice aimed at improving their
OL,19,Fperformance.
