OL,7,FThe IOPC said after its investigation
OL,8,Ffinished evidence was passed to the
OL,9,FCrown Prosecution Service to consider
OL,10,Fpossible charges against the officers,
OL,11,Fbut none was brought.
OL,13,FIOPC director Amanda Rowe said: "Our
OL,14,Fthoughts and sympathies remain with Mr
OL,15,FRoper's family and loved ones
OL,16,Ffollowing this tragic incident.
